                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Winds south to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h becoming light in the late evening.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="1" start-time-local="2026-07-24T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-07-25T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-07-23T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-07-24T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Slight chance of a shower. Light winds becoming westerly 15 to 25 km/h in the middle of the day. Overnight temperatures falling to between 3 and 6 with daytime temperatures reaching around 14.</text>
                <text type="uv_alert">Sun protection 11:30am to 1:20pm, UV Index predicted to reach 3 [Moderate]</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="2" start-time-local="2026-07-25T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-07-26T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-07-24T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-07-25T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Cloudy. Medium chance of showers, most likely in the morning and afternoon. Winds westerly 15 to 25 km/h becoming light in the late evening. Overnight temperatures falling to between 4 and 8 with daytime temperatures reaching around 15.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="3" start-time-local="2026-07-26T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-07-27T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-07-25T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-07-26T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Partly cloudy. Medium chance of showers, most likely in the morning and afternoon. Light winds becoming northwesterly 15 to 20 km/h during the day then becoming light during the afternoon. Overnight temperatures falling to between 5 and 8 with daytime temperatures reaching around 16.</text>
            </forecast-period>
            <forecast-period index="4" start-time-local="2026-07-27T00:00:00+09:30" end-time-local="2026-07-28T00:00:00+09:30" start-time-utc="2026-07-26T14:30:00Z" end-time-utc="2026-07-27T14:30:00Z">
                <text type="forecast">Mostly sunny day. Slight chance of a shower, most likely in the evening. Winds northerly 20 to 30 km/h turning northwesterly during the day. Overnight temperatures falling to between 4 and 8 with daytime temperatures reaching around 17.</text>
